>\n<br />\n呢啲戇鳩仔，完全喺到消磨所有人嘅耐性，助長負面情緒。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母我真係唔撚知有件咁嘅事啊嘛，碌碌下post無撚啦啦畀你屌，唔撚知唔撚得架？<br />\n<br />\n冇人知冇人提咁咪你提話人知囉我屌你老母，你知又唔撚講其他人唔知又可以點撚樣講啊？<br />\n<br />\n接收資訊嗰個一定要畀發放資訊嗰個屌架？<br />\n<br />\n係咪你細個你老竇教你寫字嗰陣一路教一路屌你老母先教到你呢啲撚樣出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪谷鳩氣"},{"pid":"f68125a5c739bb23b1f46032a206db41e6522f51","tid":2321200,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"基沙文屌打"},{"pid":"eae4f9f80088c774d6838d2cf0211000b485d596","tid":2321200,"uid":228487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9aff355d1bc19fce14f74f91a067603872555c0","tid":2321200,"uid":202095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZj4mzT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZj4mzT.gif&h=e71c93ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s go 唔黃<br />\n祝佢開季斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"屌你 個gif笑到我仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f506b7379e9f7c6dd2988c2959b5ac41f588b0","tid":2321200,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryWiruC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryWiruC.gif&h=86ec391b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}